# arma 3 html exporter
 Exports mods id from .html presets files into .txt files
 
 1. Name yours <name>.html file to preset.html and launch Exporter.exe
 2. Enjoy ready id file which you can copy to yours server.

Example:
@463939057:463939057
@773131200:773131200
